<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="AAP5">
<l>pāra māyapa ḻaviṉai paṟṟaṟut teṉṉaittaṉ</l>
<l>vāra mākkivait tāṉvaitta taṉṟiyeṉṉuḷ pukuntāṉ</l>
<l>kōra māta vañcey taṉaṉko laṟiyē ṉaraṅkat tammāṉṟiru</l>
<l>vāra mārpataṉ ṟōvaṭi yēṉai yāṭkoṇṭatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Severing the grips of burdensome ancient karman, He made</l>
<l>me partial to Him. Other than doing [that], He entered me.</l>
<l>Have I performed a great, dreadful penance [for this]? I do not know.</l>
<l>Is it not the chest of the Lord of Raṅgam with Śrī [and] a pearl necklace,</l>
<l rend="indent">which made me, a servant, [His] servant?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
